Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.15,0:01:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you would never have enough money to get what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.84,0:01:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Your common sense has quite a limited strike-zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.78,0:01:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, a normal person wouldn't have that kind of common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people that don't go for just the figures,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,they try to go for specific cards, too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:01:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you distinguish between cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't they all weigh the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been many legends and myths about this ever since they were introduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how certain areas have better cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,or how there are specific marks or patterns you can look for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, I can usually get the special cards I want,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,when it comes to little food packs like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a certain pattern if the box was just opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty crazy if you think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but I just can't bring myself to praise her for something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But if people have ways of knowing these things,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.56,0:02:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,don't the good ones get taken right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.03,0:02:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you live in an area with a master,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,all the rare cards and secret figures are gone in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When I go to the store to find it looks like a leaf devoured by bugs,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm left in despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I always keep that sliver of hope, thinking, "Maybe this time!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite troublesome at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Troublesome indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't there also collectors who just buy the whole box in bulk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.21,0:02:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When you buy in bulk, it's a lot easier to complete the set.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.21,0:02:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's easier to read the distribution patterns that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a fact?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But they call this the "adult purchasing method" since it's a strain on your budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Not something a part-timer like me can pull off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be called the "adult purchasing method",
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but what they're doing seems pretty childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how they want to be unique,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,or exhibit selfish behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe a "large kid purchasing method" would be a better option?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I the only one who thinks it would be better...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...to direct that passion towards something more productive?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,topics on Akihabara have gotten a lot more media attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and not for the best of reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see any problems with covering Akihabara,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's just that their depiction isn't the most flattering or accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they probably exaggerate some stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but the stories had to originate from somewhere, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't explain how TV dramas and music,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that were first popularized by the otaku-culture, have caught on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Even news programs and variety shows use anime and game music all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe they thought normal people wouldn't make the connection when they used it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of otaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Male otaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...are always talking about how they would prefer to have a girl otaku as a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,On message boards and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:04:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But you never hear a girl otaku wanting to go out with a male otaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe girls are more vulnerable to the 2D images than guys are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they're just worried about their future?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I'm sure most of them have jobs and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, why are you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that it's gotten hot, more of them have started to appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so noisy and quick to escape, I can't stand them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're dirty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It is said that Miyamoto Musashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...could catch flies with his chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,For real!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you touch those things with your eating utensils?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your concern?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I kind of understand what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Abeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never smack a mosquito.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just gross when you squish it and get blood all over your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what would you do if a mosquito landed on your arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd go, "Shoo! Shoo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Or try to blow it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you contract your muscles when a mosquito bites you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,it can't pull out its stinger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You are already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've already been bitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you contract even more,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the mosquito explodes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It itches!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.94,0:05:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It itches so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've just smacked it when you had the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san, are you going overseas again this summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think we'll be visiting our relatives in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I also often go to the summer festival with the neighbor's daughter from Ryouou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's like a little sister to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're going to the summer festival, Iwasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably look dazzling in a yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you're trying to compliment me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but somehow I can't appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you're telling me I don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Be right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You just woke up!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What a slob!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, something's been on my mind lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, did my alarm go off?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is someone else turning it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When you notice it, the switch's turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Though when noon comes around, it gets so hot that you just can't stay in bed anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way past noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kona-chan."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's morning."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"Wake up."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"Izumi-kun."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let's have lunch together."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"I was thinking about walking home with you, Konata-kun."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are the main characters in these games...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...so popular for no apparent reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably because it would be hard to make a game otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Geez!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"You'd better do your homework!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:07:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"I-It's not like I'm worried about you or anything..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Fine."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"If you say so, I'll do it."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are the heroines in these games...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...always so cute with good personalities, but lack boyfriends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys should be all over them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably because if they had boyfriends, there wouldn't be a game to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I came over to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I was here to check up on Yutaka, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nee-san, good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father is calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yutaka started on her homework, so can I borrow some manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata, don't you have to study?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you been playing this entire time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have a bad timing and happen to come every time I'm taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But that just means you take a lot of breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And so,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little worried about my image around the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep trying to stay at my desk,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't help taking a break in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you don't have good study habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not like I don't understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You've had a similar experience, Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,if I start a book that I'm really interested in during break,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and then try to study again, I can't get my mind off the book and end up taking another break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to stop in the middle of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Like with manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You tell yourself that you'll stop after just one more volume,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but before you realize it, you've read through dozens of volumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Or when you borrow the DVDs for a drama so you can watch the episodes you missed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't resist watching the next episode, and then it's downhill from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you actually watch it, it ends up being pretty stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,30)}"I see."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,30)}"Director, about this doll..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, can I change the channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't really watching, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,30)}"Where did it come from?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you wanted to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're having a special on sweets from all around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You have quite the sweet tooth, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Kagami and Tsukasa will be watching, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,30)}"It's like the Hare Hare Dance of sweets!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But most of the time, with these shows,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,even if you see something good,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it ends up being sold somewhere far away, so you're left disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We live in Saitama, so Nagoya is kind of... {kind of what?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:08:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like that most of the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but I still end up watching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.11,0:09:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sad. {Or "It's unfortunate."}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.76,0:09:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the dentist yesterday, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You were still going to the dentist?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran away in the middle of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let me know if it hurts."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"It'll be over soon."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It was something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they just don't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts just hearing about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We already have summer classes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but for them to assign homework on top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,that's going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What a waste of my summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you ever do it yourself in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.09,0:09:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,unlike elementary school or middle school,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,there aren't any independent study projects or book reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're better off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to answer questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we had to make crafts and posters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,For stuff like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you had your parents to help you out with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And then they would get so into it that they'd finish it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've won an award with something like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.46,0:10:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It was for one of my posters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all thanks to Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him I was really impressed and he was really happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that when they're supposed to get mad at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"You'd better buy at least five at a time!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I see this commercial,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I always get jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was little,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and read that story about a house made of gingerbread,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to eat as much candy as I could!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.76,0:10:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you actually get so much of your favorite thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you tend to lose interest in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it stunk all year round!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,summer homework is such a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...because I always tell myself to do it all at once in the latter half.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That was random.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought that was obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If I worked at it a little at a time over the entire summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,then maybe I wouldn't have to panic near the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And you just realized that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a third-year now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of it while you've still got that mindset, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be coming over tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and bring you a little something, too, so let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you meant by "a little at a time"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you intend to come over all summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say about once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.63,0:11:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't agree more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The A/C is on in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are making yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Every year it's like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like doing anything, and summer just passes by.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And before I know it, summer vacation is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop saying such depressing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you actually set some goals for this summer and get your homework done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,every year before summer vacation starts, I always tell myself that I'm going to work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Really now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in manga,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:12:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the "I didn't do my homework" plot is used a lot this time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When you look at it like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,it makes you think that it's the norm,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and you start to question whether you should even do your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Since that's what everyone else is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it's not okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to have that kind of attitude, don't come over in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thirsty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go get some barley tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you grab the math problem sets on my desk while you're at it, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.92,0:12:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite unpleasant to leave an air-conditioned room,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so when someone's about to leave the room, you try to get them to take care of your errands, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But then everyone ends up not wanting to step outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And in winter you don't want to leave the kotasu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,so you ask someone else to do stuff for you when they get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure is hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought some ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Choose whichever one you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And take it off my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I won't really be much help with the homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Marimokkori's eyes were just... {just what?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:12:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it that at times like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...you always wish you had the one that someone else chose?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm reading this manga right now about getting into Tokyo U.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Reading something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...makes me think that even I could make it into Tokyo U!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If I try hard like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite simpleminded of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that method could get you into Tokyo U,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd need friends who will ditch their classes to help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Teachers who hold classes like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who will take charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And a bunch of other things for it to work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it wouldn't work out that nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There are quite a few of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,People who get influenced by manga or TV dramas,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and then think they can easily change themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I do try to work hard and study,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but I keep on falling asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know any good ways to stay awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear it's better to take a quick nap, rather than forcing yourself to stay awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that one before, too, so I tried it out for myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:13:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But my quick naps always turn into good night's sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No willpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yutaka-chan, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Yu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ask us anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,One of my friends from middle school apparently has a boyfriend now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And so she asked me what she should give him as a present for his birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The atmosphere is so heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, Yu-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,there are places on the Internet where people discuss stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you check them out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There might be a thread about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use my computer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I guess I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I know about Dens** Otoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.55,0:14:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't know they had threads for stuff like this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty common, nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything goes these days, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be surprised if I found answers to questions in textbooks as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me think how easy elementary and middle school kids have it, nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As technology and the community advances,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the users' mindset and willpower become worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, that's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just supposed to copy the homework...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But unlike before,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,in the presence of an audience, it's like my pride is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, what about the summer festival at your place, Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just like last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We had to study for exams,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and if we told you, we knew you would want to come,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,so we didn't participate either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to come all the way to our festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you just go to the one where you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is that one over, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My local one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when was that again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,there are people who make a big fuss about festivals in other places,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but are completely oblivious to the ones where they live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you also the type of person who doesn't want to meet their local friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.98,0:15:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because we're college applicants doesn't mean we can study for exams 24/7! {24/7? Lol.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,there is going to be a fireworks festival near my house tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:15:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we all go out and have fun for once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We could use a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,tsn't there going to be a fireworks festival near your house tomorrow, Minami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see Japanese fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all go together and check it out, Minami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Minami-chan, are you free tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's decided, Minami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Iwasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Iwasaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pretty famous fireworks festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Iwasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you call someone a certain way, it's hard to give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's pretty far away and famous, so I'm sure a lot of people will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-chan, will you be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you have a cold until just recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be pretty hot tomorrow, so do you want to wait for the next one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I, the nurse's assistant, will be with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:16:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yutaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Minami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we decided to go see the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,With all this college exam preparation, there hasn't been much time to do fun stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Kagami and the others are all serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You should just do what you want, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to drag Kanata around with me everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And we made lots of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Though she got pretty mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You just can't let your youth slip by!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe I should get a boyfriend and make some memories myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never accept a boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not making any sense, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to come watch the fireworks with us, Yu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,To hear something like that from Konata...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I'm going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As a father, this hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're meeting at Minami-chan's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want her to follow in our footsteps...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The train's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.08,0:17:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yutaka-chan came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.07,0:18:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Patricia-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys here for the fireworks, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.37,0:18:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You look really good in a yutaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So Miyuki-san's neighbor was Minami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Help yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we miss someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you count yourself, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,9.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for having us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is Minami-chan's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A huge dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't bark at all, and it's pretty friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they're big, if they're like that, then they seem so much cuter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's growling at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's the type who just gets barked at for no reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When you were little,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,did you ever wonder if fireworks still looked round from the side?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't look flat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes they show fireworks displays on TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but it definitely feels different when you see them in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time they fire a huge one,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and announce, "This was brought to you by,"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,followed by the name of some business or store,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't that ruin the mood for you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-chan, you look a little pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, so you guys go watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Minami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what summer is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.25,0:20:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not all beautiful memories like in a manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I got bitten everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so itchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They say it itches more if you scratch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you take off your yukata,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the belt mark on your stomach gets really itchy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sorry I caused you so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you guys get bitten by mosquitoes, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't get bitten at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So some people get bitten by mosquitoes more easily than others?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe the mosquito could read the atmosphere...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oha-lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your navigator, Kogami Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.80,0:21:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the assistant,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.24,0:21:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ono Daisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been fast, but Lucky Channel is on its 20th episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a crow today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're not a dog today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.92,0:21:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let us have a look at the live feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... I wonder where he is right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that Shiroishi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mt. Fuji is so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.87,0:21:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bii!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.08,0:21:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bii!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiraishi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiraishi-kun!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what you wanted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Shiraishi Minoru here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:21:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, please listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.53,0:22:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Bridegroom Rumba!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.45,0:22:20.20,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Romaji} Shiawase no koe hibiku...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.20,0:22:23.74,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Romaji} Rokugatsu no kyoukai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.74,0:22:27.48,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Romaji} Shiawase no zecchou wa...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.96,0:22:31.73,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Romaji} Masa ni kono toki
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.73,0:22:35.33,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Romaji} Ah, konna koto ni naru no naru...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:38.76,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Romaji} Ikko date nante kawanakya yokatta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.76,0:22:42.68,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Romaji} Hanayome ni nigerareru nante...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:46.23,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Romaji} Manga mitai na situation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:49.72,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Romaji} Awatete Omuko Rumba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:51.81,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Romaji} Dare ka tasukete...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:22:53.53,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Both} Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:57.15,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Romaji} Kore kara dou suru no?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.15,0:23:01.08,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Romaji} Joushi mo kiteru no ni!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:02.26,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Both} 1 . 2 . 3
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:03.26,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Both} 2 . 2 . 3
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.26,0:23:06.27,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{Kara Romaji} Omuko Rumba!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.45,0:22:20.20,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} Merry voices ring through the air...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.20,0:22:23.74,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} ...at a church in June.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.74,0:22:27.48,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} The phrase "happiest moment of my life" was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.96,0:22:31.73,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} ...made for such a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.73,0:22:35.33,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} If I'd known this would happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:38.76,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} ...I wouldn't have bought that new house.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.76,0:22:42.68,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} Getting jilted by the bride...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:46.23,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} ...is like something out of manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:49.72,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} All worked up, I break into the Bridegroom Rumba.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:51.81,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} Somebody save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:22:53.53,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:57.15,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} What am I going to do now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.15,0:23:01.08,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} Even my boss is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.26,0:23:06.27,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara} Bridegroom Rumba!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.96,0:23:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And next week on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.27,0:23:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Misao here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.03,0:23:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayano here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.79,0:23:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ayano.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.77,0:23:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Hiiragi so cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She always runs off to that shorty's class, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.48,0:23:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Does our love not reach her?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.50,0:23:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Next week: "Pandora's Box"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.65,0:23:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayano's cold, too...
